{"tid":439081,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門公路私家車應該收費 收益補貼巴士兩蚊","createTime":"2017-10-17T13:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T14:07:08.000Z","uid":77905,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6f7b4276e3cb93fd99de9bcb41a82a6daf15e6","tid":439081,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"跟據2013年屯門公路早上繁忙時間的車輛組合數據：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1）私家車佔 44% 及的士佔 7%<br />\n換言之以上兩種路面利用效率最低之車輛已佔過半流量，載客只佔一成多<br />\n<br />\n2）相反巴士佔車流量僅12%，但運載人數卻係八成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，條路有50%流量係私家車，但載嘅人只係當中嘅一成幾<br />\n巴士佔一成車流量，但係佢講嘅係載住八成人返工返屋企<br />\n更唔好講好多濕勁嘅司機炒車jam死晒成條屯公／荃灣路／汀九<br />\n繁忙時間條路已經慢，車速分別本身都唔大<br />\n用私家車的士行屯公跟本就無優勢，反而拖晒成條路落水慢車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇睇2013年車流數據：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屯門公路荃灣方向 <br />\n早上繁忙時間(0730-0930) 每小時 5 000 架次<br />\n<br />\n屯門公路往屯門方向<br />\n晚上繁忙時間 (1800-2000) 每小時 4 800 架次<br />\n<br />\n每程私家車如果 繁忙時間收費25蚊<br />\n20 000架次 x 50% x $25 = $ 250 000 / 日<br />\n非繁忙時間私家車收費15蚊<br />\n100 000架次 x 50% x $15 = $ 750 000 / 日 <br />\n<br />\n當每日屯門公路巴士乘客係30萬人次<br />\n$ 1 000 000 / 300 000 人次，一程車可以補貼到3蚊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當每日坐968返工，當一個月936蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟據今年施政報告有134蚊補貼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果屯門公路私家車收費，每程巴士補貼3蚊，一個月就慳成600蚊<br />\n即使有2／3收入用做行政費 都仲做到200蚊補貼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門公路私家車收費成效就係<br />\n1）減少塞車<br />\n2）減少大西北交通費<br />\n<br />\n而收費方式則應該用唔洗停車嘅方法，呢層外國其實大把技術 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cf3b2ce0094d8d5dc106b5262522a1d3ea9320","tid":439081,"uid":79154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:33:19.000Z","msg":"咁樣咪塞死下路"},{"pid":"f2dae1194babaa518413a65c1e20408bcf86b38c","tid":439081,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"大欖即加$20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228a69c757552560db47066b3a5a983a6839b36e","tid":439081,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣咪塞死下路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獅隧收費唔會塞大埔道"},{"pid":"2cc2a848e943c35501d2a12c0b34cf25aa043456","tid":439081,"uid":33336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:43:33.000Z","msg":"炒車罰司機一萬！<br />\n<br />\n原因：引致嚴重塞車"},{"pid":"4bd2c4acda82494cedfda0e763845d1446e6b810","tid":439081,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T23:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df276cea86b5572bc11ae9ba7be7abbd8f726b5a","tid":439081,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T23:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒車罰司機一萬！<br />\n<br />\n原因：引致嚴重塞車</blockquote><br />\n我仲絕<br />\n每行車綫每公里罰1000"},{"pid":"2b6222c4442bfc000d32aabb02b5719ee3c3f684","tid":439081,"uid":9942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炒車罰司機一萬！<br />\n<br />\n原因：引致嚴重塞車</blockquote><br />\n我仲絕<br />\n每行車綫每公里罰1000</blockquote><br />\n講到你真係罰到人錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba210316f1e69fe0d54a2c212a421d2001e819b","tid":439081,"uid":73092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T23:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒車罰司機一萬！<br />\n<br />\n原因：引致嚴重塞車</blockquote><br />\n應該永久停牌"},{"pid":"51652635b3cda5498ca62a34225fa0ac3e6c6e95","tid":439081,"uid":77905,"li